summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of WalkInSquare retail portfolio website. All core features working correctly including navigation, outlet displays, gallery, contact form, and responsive design.
passed_tests: Hero section loads with proper styling and CTA buttons work
Navigation links smooth scroll to correct sections
Stats section displays correct numbers (50 total, 12 operational, 38 upcoming)
About section renders with image and content
Running Outlets section displays 12 outlets in bento grid layout
Upcoming Outlets section displays outlets with 'View All 38 Outlets' button functionality
Contact form inputs work and ready for mailto functionality
Footer renders with links and contact info
Responsive design works on desktop, tablet, and mobile viewports
Hero CTA buttons navigate to correct sections
Contact form can be filled and is ready for mailto submission
